Show HN: A simple, high-speed price betting platform on crypto
text: You bet on the direction of a crypto price in the next 60 secs (up/down). If you're right, you can win >60%, if you're wrong, you lose your investment. Onboard just with an ETH transfer, no KYC, no trading fees. Fun mode available.

Ask HN: Best Webcam These Days?
text:
I'm looking for a webcam to replace my nearly decade-old Logitech C920, which washes out color and has a middling mic.

I don't care as much about resolution as autofocus quality and high/low light performance and color balance.

It needs to work in Linux. (Most do, from what I can tell.). Any recommendations?
